Interface HashMap<K,V>

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    HashMap.AbstractNode, HashMap.ArrayNode, HashMap.EmptyNode, HashMap.IndexedNode, HashMap.LeafNode

    public interface HashMap<K,V>
    A HashMap implementation based on a Hash array mapped trie (HAMT).
